emailcontent.subject: Your Account Access Has Been Limited

body.content:
<head>
<title>PayPal - Limited Account Access Details</title><meta http-equiv="description" content="PayPal lets you send money to anyone with email. PayPal is free for consumers and works seamlessly with your existing credit card and checking account. You can settle debts, borrow cash, divide bills or split expenses with friends all without going to an ATM or looking for your checkbook."><meta http-equiv="keywords" content="Send, money, payments, credit, credit card, instant, money, financial services, mobile, wireless, WAP, cell phones, two-way pagers, Windows CE">
